ORLANDO Pirates have lost their 12th man. The prominent man who is seen wearing with powder on his face and head at Pirates matches Mandla 'Mgijimi' Sindane has passed away. Mgijimi as he is affectionately known in the football circles, passed away on Tuesday in his home in Witbank , Mpumalanga. Details around his death are still sketchy. More to follow...  Sad news about #Mgijimi, a passionate football man with a good heart too. Hamba kahle Magebhula. #MHSRIP pic.twitter.com/lnLsLR5Li2 